metadata.description:
Welcome to MJWWT!  
This AI artwork is set in the future of Steampunk, a world line where steam engines thrive!  
Wishing for a peaceful world, alive and having fun with all the diversity of personalities.  
Now, join the MJWWT parade that loves diversity, connects, and imagines a whole new level of fun!
